低于 93，就应及时就医检查。如果没有备的话可以，也可以观察症状，如果高烧超过 3 天，呼吸急促，每分钟大于 30 次，说明肺功能下降，应及时就医，否则很容易转成危重症。热搜！阳后有必要拍肺部 CT 吗？一直咳会不会得肺炎？不吃药硬扛，这两种情况要特别小心… | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe65284c2ee697253e0af8540aa56e55_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/574927684"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IoN+W7NCukIAgEAMaCDkwMDQzMTUwILyMqZ0GMAI46wJALnIJNTc0OTI3Njg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1672182252.2341876", "card_id": "Q_574833407", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《三体》电视剧版怎么制作才能避免动画版的口碑滑坡？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c9ea6fff644aafcfa1d1fe419c3cd54c_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/574833407"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IoN+W7NCukIAgEAMaCDkwMDIyMzQ0INOipp0GMAY4OkAvcgk1NzQ4MzM0MDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1672182252.2347128", "card_id": "Q_563637135", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "结婚之后该与婆家、娘家保持怎样的距离才算刚刚好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-bba38db243953a8d7c9f2c2716b247eb_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D",